H0.text: Gluteus medius, Gluteus maximus and Piriformis are muscles in human. Hamstring

H1.text: Gluteus medius, Gluteus maximus and Piriformis are muscles in human. Iliopsoas

H2.text: Gluteus medius, Gluteus maximus and Piriformis are muscles in human. Psoas major

H3.text: Gluteus medius, Gluteus maximus and Piriformis are muscles in human. Tuch

A4.text: The gluteus maximus is a muscle that covers the posterior third of the gluteus medius.

A5.text: The piriformis is a muscle that may be closely united to the posterior border of the gluteus medius.
